Texts.Chs: 用以太玻璃制成的木质窗格。
Texts.Eng: A window with wooden panes, made of Aetheric Glass.

Texts.Chs: 现在我可以透过星星看星星，就像一颗星星。
Texts.Eng: Now I can look at the stars through stars, as a star.

Texts.Chs: 漂亮的窗户，叶族人可以看到外面。
Texts.Eng: Pretty windowss, Floran can see outside.

Texts.Chs: 这扇窗户有助于使房间明亮起来，就好像不是木头一样。
Texts.Eng: This window helps brighten the room, as if the wood didn't.
